{"word":"ἀλύσκω","slug":"ἀλύσκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀλύσκω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀλύω'><el>ἀλύω</el></a>\n<p/><i>to flee from, shun, avoid, forsake</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: rarely <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>to flee from</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>:— <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to escape</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/>"}]}